ir official website.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9774534267153389, \"rank\": 0.014986257279368283, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"their official website\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Rather than trying to look beyond the traditional colours, we decided to embrace them and push the iconic red, white and blue as far as we could.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the traditional colours\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Parade your pride for our country and the hard working athletes by displaying in any bedroom or flagpole.\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your pride\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"the hard working athletes\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"any bedroom\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"flagpole\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Create a show stopper, fit for any fan.'\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a show stopper\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"any fan\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whitbread, who won a javelin silver medal at the 1988 Games, will not be purchasing the new-look flag and was left 'disgusted'.\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Whitbread\", \"score\": 0.9999756646285062, \"rank\": 